                  King <persName ref="PRS3429DawitII">Dāwit II</persName>, ʾabbā <persName ref="PRS4709Giyorgis">
                     Giyorgis of Saglā</persName> and King 
                  <persName ref="PRS10626ZaraY">Zarʾa Yāʿqob</persName>. It is the name of the author of several texts. </floruit>
       
               
